{{Infobox medical condition (new) | name = 心肌炎 | image = Viral myocarditis (1).JPG | caption = 一个患有急性心脏病的人的心肌炎显微镜[[尸检]]照片 | field = [[心臟病學]] | synonyms = 炎症性心肌病 | symptoms = [[呼吸困难]]、{{tsl|en|chest pain|胸口疼痛}}、运动能力降低、[[心律不整]]<ref name=NEJM2009/> | complications =[[心搏停止]]、[[扩张型心肌病]]引发的[[心臟衰竭]]<ref name=NEJM2009/> | onset = | duration = 几小时至几个月不等<ref name=NEJM2009/> | types = | causes = 一般由[[病毒感染]]引起，但也可因[[病原细菌|病原细菌感染]]、特定的药物、毒素、[[自體免疫性疾病]]引起<ref name=NEJM2009/><ref name=Kin2012>{{cite journal|last1=Kindermann|first1=I|last2=Barth|first2=C|last3=Mahfoud|first3=F|last4=Ukena|first4=C|last5=Lenski|first5=M|last6=Yilmaz|first6=A|last7=Klingel|first7=K|last8=Kandolf|first8=R|last9=Sechtem|first9=U|last10=Cooper|first10=LT|last11=Böhm|first11=M|title=Update on myocarditis.|journal=Journal of the American College of Cardiology|date=2012-02-28|volume=59|issue=9|pages=779–92|pmid=22361396|doi=10.1016/j.jacc.2011.09.074}}</ref> | risks = | diagnosis = [[心电图]]、血液[[肌钙蛋白]]、[[心血管磁共振成像]]、心脏活检<ref name=NEJM2009/><ref name=Kin2012/> | differential = | prevention = | treatment = 药物、{{tsl|en|implantable cardiac defibrillator|植入式心律去颤器}}、[[心脏移植]]<ref name=NEJM2009/><ref name=Kin2012/> | medication = [[血管紧张肽I转化酶抑制剂]], [[Β受体阻断药]], [[利尿劑]], [[皮質類固醇]], [[静脉注射免疫球蛋白]]<ref name=NEJM2009/><ref name=Kin2012/> | prognosis = | frequency = 加上[[心肌病]]共250万（2015年）<ref name=GBD2015Pre>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2015 Disease and Injury Incidence and Prevalence|first1=Collaborators.|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 310 diseases and injuries, 1990-2015: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2015.|journal=Lancet (London, England)|date=2016-10-08|volume=388|issue=10053|pages=1545-1602|pmid=27733282}}</ref> | deaths = 加上心肌病共35.4万（2015年）<ref name=GBD2015De>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2015 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators.|title=Global, regional, and national life expectancy, all-cause mortality, and cause-specific mortality for 249 causes of death, 1980-2015: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2015.|journal=Lancet (London, England)|date=2016-10-08|volume=388|issue=10053|pages=1459-1544|pmid=27733281}}</ref>
}} {{medical}} {{distinguish|心肌梗塞}} '''心肌炎'''（{{lang-la|Myocarditis}}），也称为'''炎症性心肌病'''（{{lang|en|Inflammatory Cardiomyopathy}}），是[[心肌]]的[[炎症]]。症状可表现为[[呼吸困难]]、{{tsl|en|chest pain|胸口疼痛}}、运动能力降低、[[心律不整]]等。发病时长可从几小时至几个月不等。并发症包括[[心搏停止]]或[[扩张型心肌病]]引发的[[心臟衰竭]]。<ref name=NEJM2009>{{cite journal|last1=Cooper LT|first1=Jr|title=Myocarditis.|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|date=2009-04-09|volume=360|issue=15|pages=1526–38|pmid=19357408|doi=10.1056/nejmra0800028}}</ref>
最常引起心肌炎的原因是[[病毒]]感染<ref name="NEJM2009" />。其他原因包括[[細菌感染]]、藥物、毒素和[[自體免疫性疾病]]<ref name="NEJM2009" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Update on myocarditis|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22361396|last=Kindermann|first=Ingrid|last2=Barth|first2=Christine|date=2012-02-28|journal=Journal of the American College of Cardiology|issue=9|doi=10.1016/j.jacc.2011.09.074|volume=59|pages=779–792|issn=1558-3597|pmid=22361396|last3=Mahfoud|first3=Felix|last4=Ukena|first4=Christian|last5=Lenski|first5=Matthias|last6=Yilmaz|first6=Ali|last7=Klingel|first7=Karin|last8=Kandolf|first8=Reinhard|last9=Sechtem|first9=Udo}}</ref>。診斷方法是使用[[心電圖]]、[[肌钙蛋白|肌鈣蛋白]]上升、[[心血管磁共振成像]]，有時候也會進行心臟活體組織切片。很重要的是需要先透過以[[心臟超音波]]排除[[心瓣|心臟瓣膜]]問題<ref name="NEJM2009" /><ref name=":0" />。
治療方法依嚴重程度和致病原因而決定。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="NEJM2009" />常用的藥物包括[[血管紧张素|血管張力素]]轉換酶抑制劑、乙型阻斷劑、[[利尿劑]]。復原期間不建議運動。[[類固醇]]和人類[[免疫球蛋白]]靜脈注射劑在某些情況有用。情況嚴重者可能建議植入式心臟復律除顫器或進行心臟移植。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="NEJM2009" />
在2013年，急性心肌炎發生案例約有150萬件<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 301 acute and chronic diseases and injuries in 188 countries, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26063472|last=Global Burden of Disease Study 2013 Collaborators|date=2015-08-22|journal=Lancet (London, England)|issue=9995|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(15)60692-4|volume=386|pages=743–800|issn=1474-547X|pmc=4561509|pmid=26063472}}</ref>。心肌炎不分年齡皆會發生，但年輕族群更常發生，而男性比例略高於女性<ref name="NEJM2009" />。多數案例病情輕微<ref name=":0" />。在2015年時，[[心肌症]]（其中也包括了[[心肌炎]]）<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/867317527|title=Cellular and Molecular Pathobiology of Cardiovascular Disease|last=S.,|first=Willis, Monte|last2=W.,|first2=Homeister, Jonathon|last3=1967-|first3=Stone, James R.,|publisher=|year=|isbn=9780124055254|location=London|pages=|chapter=|oclc=867317527}}</ref>造成35.4萬人死亡，較1990年的29.4萬人要多。最早對心肌炎的描述出現在1800年代的中期。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/150948676|title=Infectious diseases in critical care medicine|last=A.|first=Cunha, Burke|date=2007|publisher=Informa Healthcare|year=|isbn=9781420019605|edition=2nd ed|location=New York|pages=|chapter=|oclc=150948676}}</ref>
